shows you how to setup a simple PHP application structure and connect to a PostgreSQL database.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/create-tables\/\">Creating new PostgreSQL database tables<\/a> &#8211; walks you through the steps of creating database tables in PostgreSQL using PHP.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/insert\/\">Inserting data into PostgresQL tables<\/a> &#8211; guides you how to use insert data into a table&nbsp;using PHP PDO.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/update\/\">Updating data in the table<\/a> &#8211; provides you with the steps of updating data in the database tables.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/query\/\">Querying data from a table<\/a>&nbsp;&#8211; shows you various ways to query data in the PostgreSQL database from PHP.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/transaction\/\">Performing transactions<\/a> &#8211; explains the transaction concept and shows you how to perform transactions in PHP.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/postgresql-blob\/\">Working with the binary large objects (BLOB)<\/a> &#8211; shows you how to insert, select, and delete the large objects in the PostgreSQL using PHP.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/call-stored-procedures\/\">Calling PostgreSQL stored procedures<\/a> &#8211; explains you the steps of calling <a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-stored-procedures\/\">PostgreSQL stored procedures<\/a> from PHP.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.postgresqltutorial.com\/postgresql-php\/delete\/\">Deleting data in a PostgreSQL table using PHP PDO<\/a> &#8211; teaches you how to delete data from the PostgreSQL table in the PHP application using PDO.<\/li><\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This section shows you h